{"type": "article", "id": 45361, "title": "Zara 在印度推电商，以及，Nike 发布环保皮革材质 Flyleather | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-09-20T03:31:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 44203, "name": "flyleather"}, {"id": 44204, "name": "腰包"}, {"id": 18579, "name": "OFF-WHITE"}, {"id": 16651, "name": "Timberland"}, {"id": 44205, "name": "zara"}, {"id": 5522, "name": "历峰"}, {"id": 2836, "name": "Victoria Beckham"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170920111111zARJQTP5UBgdSprO.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://jingdaily.com/jin-keyu-richemont-chinese-board-member/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>历峰集团的董事会里第一次出现了一位中国人：金刻羽</strong></a> | 金刻羽的父亲是首任亚投行行长金立群。在成为董事会成员以前，金刻羽是历峰集团咨询委员会成员，并不拥有实权。今年历峰集团经历了历史上最大幅度的高层变动。CEO Richard Lepeu 和 CFO Gary Saage 均先后退休，随后被寄予继任厚望的腕表主管 Georges Kern 也在今年 7 月去了历峰的对手集团 Breitling。现在，所有主管均直接向董事会直接汇报。目前董事会共有 19 位不同国籍的董事。</p><p><a href=\"https://qz.com/1076219/by-going-online-in-india-zara-itx-can-finally-reach-fashion-forward-shoppers-outside-the-metros/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Zara 计划于 10 月 4 日在印度推出电商服务</strong></a> | Zara 将成为首个在印度市场上线电商的品牌。目前 Zara 在印度只有 20 个门店。据波士顿咨询报告，印度时尚市场总值 700 亿美元，而线上只占 5%，但到 2020 年该比例将提升至 12%，线上消费人数会翻一番。 </p><p><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/victoria-beckham-leads-in-digital-engagement-at-new-york-fashion-week/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>纽约时装周社交媒体话题热度公布，Victoria Beckham 最高</strong></a> | 数据分析机构 ListenFirst指出，纽约时装周期间，Victoria Beckham 品牌的热度最高，在社交媒体上一共被提及 566.2 万次，占时装周话题总量的 17%。排名紧随其后的是 Calvin Klein，第三位是 Michael Kors。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>最近，腰包很是流行，Supreme、PALACE 等街头品牌都出了大热的腰包。英国设计师 Albert Pukies 也赶了一波潮流，推出了恶趣味的啤酒肚造型腰包 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/funny-dadbag-albert-pukies\" rel=\"nofollow\">The Dadbag</a>...</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920104453ziP2tYpkFs1aw3SO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920104453tY5x3V48I7kbcASp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920104453NfIanu8pcvwtHTmZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920104453tQByNT9JY0SmwA6O.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709201044543tv42dFKBqNQwDpO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920104458Dob3wnNvmJGyiS8U.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/kappa-fw2017-banda-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kappa 公布了 2017 秋冬 BANDA 系列 </a>lookbook，复古运动设计还挺潮的。该系列将于 9 月 23 日起登陆品牌日本官网。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709201044027IiZBKE5GfTXOuvV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499145\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920104402oZXriTyv9bwqlWDp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499145\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709201044045UZOauSFmQ3gnkNp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499145\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920104404m97z2U5TMqXEuF6I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499145\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920104406nXEYcOUf4tiPQz2r.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499145\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017092010440658ajcpGKR0S7IJn3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499145\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920104407u1Z65yGgRvtLfkHJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499145\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920104408ekrhwbmnavUIPWJj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499145\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920104415g5Fw4Xj93nEaqeNk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499145\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920104415jrpqzoBEWfAkhJPR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499145\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920104416AuwPamvZUjepWzB8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499145\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920104416vB7ZXyPdOhtn2WQJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499145\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920104422L2PEHQ6v38cSrkKN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499145\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920104423Ut7jJqMlEoxRf1iQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499145\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>2017 秋冬系列，Levi’s 的高端支线<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/levis-made-crafted-aw-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Levi’s Made&amp;Crafted </a>以冰岛山河景色为灵感，好看。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920104342PNzXeuqU8sAIaOig.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498291\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920104342gwMz0O4S1rdWTYGC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499145\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920104343SBZNmqa87CGHKlMJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498291\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709201043467qB89M4uALaKXEVR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498291\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920104347IDhuMNorWEBgfAsk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498291\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920105344DzA74qkyQ5UfvYsJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498291\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920105345a9BNc6TiPzFex1Hl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498291\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920105345bnk93ROGeLNyqWQK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920105353oItZDjb4KWpw7s8y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498291\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>OFF-WHITE 与 Timberland 的全新联名款 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/off-white-timberland-6-inch-boot-closer-look\" rel=\"nofollow\">6-inch Boot </a>发布，来看看这双丝绒材质的马丁靴： </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920110031OBRbkn4rSLPiKyl8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920110030U21mZdJHY73EGvPO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920110030ZQyFJXUYLHCWMpGe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920110030ge8Acd6So49VfiEU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920110030dzxMgaDZI5XBHN0i.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>还记得今年 LV 在日本美秀博物馆的那场大秀吗？9 月 29 日至 10 月 12 日，LV 将在东京南青山开设世界唯一一家 2018 度假系列的<a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/news/2017-09-20/lv-cruise18/topics/\" rel=\"nofollow\">快闪店</a>。届时还将推出致敬山本宽斋的限定单品。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920110731MUpQilB08Tvat3Ir.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.780303\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920110730dv5PaBfYgoI9KsH3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920110731G1rFYzcMHTZQsqyl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/nike-flyleather\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nike 发布创新环保技术 Flyleather</a>。这种独特的材质由超过 50% 的回收天然皮革纤维与水制成，比普通皮革轻 40%，且耐久性更强，是普通皮革的五倍。<br></p><p>这波采用 Flyleather 制作的运动鞋 Nike Flyleather Tennis Classic 现已在 Nike soho、NikeLab 21 Mercer、Dover Street Market 上架。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920110044skfl17WMVbwg6tUr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920110044uGwy5hK4TSHZjmrb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920110044SntDicLlMoBJgHjm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920110044F3sqe2ZY4IOuVlgU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170920110045XS3acku4NPCQ85hD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"https://www.wired.com/story/nikes-flyleather-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">wired</a></p>"}